{
  "id": null,
  "uid": "invoice-tempo-traces",
  "title": "Invoice Backend - Tempo Traces",
  "tags": ["invoice", "tempo", "traces"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 1,
  "refresh": "15s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-1h",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Trace Workflow",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Use Grafana Explore with the **Tempo** datasource for full trace inspection.\n\nSuggested TraceQL queries:\n- `{}` to list recent traces\n- `{ span.http.target = \"/upload\" }` for upload endpoint\n- `{ status = error }` for failing traces\n\nPanels below show whether the trace pipeline is healthy (collector accepting and exporting spans)."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Collector Accepted Spans/s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 0, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "accepted spans/s"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Collector Exported Spans/s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 8, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_exporter_sent_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "exported spans/s"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Collector Failed Spans/s",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 8, "x": 16, "y": 5 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_exporter_send_failed_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "failed spans/s"
        }
      ],
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": { "calcs": ["lastNotNull"], "fields": "", "values": false },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Collector Trace Pipeline Throughput",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_receiver_accepted_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "accepted"
        },
        {
          "refId": "B",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_exporter_sent_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "exported"
        },
        {
          "refId": "C",
          "expr": "sum(rate(otelcol_exporter_send_failed_spans{job=\"otel-collector\"}[5m]))",
          "legendFormat": "failed"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Backend HTTP Request Rate (trace candidate load)",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 11 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "PBFA97CFB590B2093" },
      "targets": [
        {
          "refId": "A",
          "expr": "sum(rate(http_requests_total{job=\"backend\"}[5m])) by (status)",
          "legendFormat": "{{status}}"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Datasource Check",
      "gridPos": { "h": 6, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 20 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "Tempo is provisioned as datasource **Tempo**. If traces are empty, verify:\n1. `OTEL_ENABLED=true` in backend env\n2. backend exports OTLP to `otel-collector:4317`\n3. Collector forwards traces to Tempo\n4. Grafana time range includes recent requests"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 99,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "Data Source Legend",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 26 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "**This dashboard validates Tempo trace pipeline health.**\\n\\n- **Tempo traces**: backend spans exported through OTEL Collector\\n- **Prometheus stats here**: collector throughput/failure counters\\n- **Langfuse traces/scores/users**: available in Langfuse UI"
      }
    }
  ],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "annotations": {
    "list": [
      {
        "builtIn": 1,
        "datasource": { "type": "grafana", "uid": "-- Grafana --" },
        "enable": true,
        "hide": true,
        "iconColor": "rgba(0, 211, 255, 1)",
        "name": "Annotations & Alerts",
        "type": "dashboard"
      }
    ]
  }
}
